    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a practical choice for someone looking for reliable transportation at a lower price point. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a few small dings on the passenger side doors. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may require some upcoming maintenance like new tires or a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a functional car that has been used well, perfect for a daily commuter or a first-time driver who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
