    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade vehicle in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. The interior is equally immaculate; the premium leather remains supple and crease-free, the cabin retains its original new-car scent, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting\u2014operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively through authorized dealerships. The engine bay is pristine, the alloy wheels are free of curb rash, and the tires have nearly full tread remaining. This is a non-smoker, no-pet vehicle that offers a driving experience identical to the day it was first delivered. Clean title and all original keys/manuals included.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
